<section class="graduate-lead">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <p class="lead">We're launching an exciting new graduate management scheme to grow and develop passionate, inspirational leaders of the future.</p>
        <p>Over two years, you'll gain the skills, knowledge and confidence that will enable you to make real improvements at the frontline of the healthcare service and improve patient care.</p>
